    "About": "关于",
    "A showroom-first brand focused on trust, product visibility, and real customer conversations.": "以门店体验为核心，强调信任感、产品展示与真实沟通的品牌。",
    "Our Story": "我们的故事",
    "We help customers choose with confidence": "帮助顾客更安心地做选择",
    "Win Win Car Studio Accessories was built around a simple idea: customers should be able to discover products online, then speak to real people before deciding what fits their car.": "Win Win Car Studio Accessories 的理念很简单：顾客先在线了解产品，再与真实团队沟通，决定什么更适合自己的车。",
    "Starting from a small workshop in Kuala Lumpur, the team focused on practical advice, in-person product viewing, and honest recommendations instead of pushing quick online purchases.": "从吉隆坡的一间小型工作室开始，团队始终重视务实建议、到店看货与真诚推荐，而不是推动顾客仓促在线下单。",
    "Today, the website works as a trusted showcase that helps customers understand the range first, then continue the conversation in the showroom or on WhatsApp.": "如今，这个网站更像一个可信的展示窗口，让顾客先了解产品，再到门店或通过 WhatsApp 继续沟通。",
